多吃鸡鸭鹅肉，实在没钱就多吃鸡蛋，一天吃三个鸡蛋才两块钱。 培养他养成早睡习惯，让他 10 点前必须睡觉。 作业写不完，学习跟不上，不要过于苛责，能多长高十厘米，身体健康强壮，比做完功课强上百倍。 需要注意他的牙齿、坐姿、体态，有问题要及时矫正。 有空多带他爬山、跑步、晒太阳，多让他挑战自己的体能极限。 注意她青春期的皮肤问题，不要让他脸上留下痘坑、痘印。 尽量少对他发脾气。 普通家庭父母能做到这些就很完美了，进了社会就知道，身高高一些，较好的外貌，健康的身体，真的事事顺，很多机会也会多很多。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-6e8df759987fcbfe6b03bab45f72b79a.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2039438592494278578"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIosq074fLsa5rEAMaCTExOTU0NDYwMSCT4qbQBjAAOOQHQA9yEzIwMzk0Mzg1OTI0OTQyNzg1Nzh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1779393227.66725", "card_id": "Q_2037993874522629479", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 46}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "Anthropic 被曝 300 亿美元融资，投前估值超 9000 亿，AI 泡沫到底有没有天花板？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-958efcc169fd38197114fba710cbd51b.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2037993874522629479"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIosq074fLsa5rEAMaCTExOTQ5NTQ2NSCT35HQBjAAOJMBQBByEzIwMzc5OTM4NzQ1MjI2Mjk0Nzl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1779393227.66926", "card_id": "Q_2039755382055294649", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 41}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "穆里尼奥已经在多支球队执教不成功了，为什么 2026 年皇马还要签他？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-4c6b276aee1301be20a95e2d9e215c02_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color